  Time Complexity:
Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division → O(1)
Factorial → O(n)
Overall worst case → O(n)
  Space Complexity: O(1)
  Worst Case Scenario: When the user repeatedly chooses the factorial option with a very large input, requiring n multiplications each time.
